This directory includes matlab interface of the curvelet transform
using wrapping.

Basic functions
	fdct_wrapping.m -- forward curvelet transform
	ifdct_wrapping.m -- inverse curvelet transform
	fdct_wrapping_param.m -- returns the location of each curvelet in phase-space

Useful tools
	fdct_wrapping_dispcoef.m -- returns a matrix containing all curvelet coefficients
	fdct_wrapping_pos2idx.m -- for fixed scale and fixed direction, returns
		the curvelet which is closest to a certain point on the image

Demos
	fdct_wrapping_demo_basic.m -- display the shape of a curvelet
	fdct_wrapping_demo_recon.m -- partial reconstruction using curvelet
	fdct_wrapping_demo_disp.m -- display all the curvelet coefficients of an image
	fdct_wrapping_demo_denoise.m -- image denoising using curvelet
